      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test fluid (bovine blood) is representative of clinical human blood for hemolysis index purposes.",
      "rationale": "Bovine blood is the standard surrogate for hemolysis bench testing per ASTM F1841. Acceptable at MRL 2 without further sample characterisation study."
    },
